      "title": "5-year work visa for foreigners employed at BOI-registered Sri Lankan firms",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign nationals serving in BOI-registered companies in Sri Lanka as owners, directors and other high officials, will be provided with 05 years Working Visa from tomorrow (July 01), says Minister Dhammika Perera."
      ],
